87
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:13,639
Keep an eye on Dongfang Chen.

88
00:05:14,639 --> 00:05:15,879
He's way too close to the blast.

89
00:05:15,879 --> 00:05:17,040
It could be dangerous.

