his only attachment was Bai Zhitao.)

94
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:30,000
(She saved him and protected him.)

95
00:05:30,439 --> 00:05:32,160
(So Bai Zhitao should be on set too.)

96
00:05:37,160 --> 00:05:38,680
(Only the hero and heroine matter.)

97
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:41,600
(Everyone else is supposed
to sacrifice for their love.)

98
00:05:42,279 --> 00:05:44,040
(Does showcasing heroine's kindness)

99
00:05:44,279 --> 00:05:45,680
(mean Dongfang Chen
has to be disfigured,)

100
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:46,600
(or even die?)

101
00:05:47,399 --> 00:05:50,160
(The sacrifices of
a side character for the leads' romance)

102
00:05:50,399 --> 00:05:52,160
(are what stick with the audience.)

103
00:05:52,279 --> 00:05:53,759
(This is the so-called BE aesthetic.)

104
00:06:03,870 --> 00:06:05,390
I refuse to suffer
for the sake of suffering.

105
00:06:06,260 --> 00:06:07,839
I won't let Bai Zhitao
become collateral damage.

106
